An extension that allows you to activate a Proxy for clicking on links of the *.ton and *.adnl type.
With this extension, you can activate a proxy server to follow links like *.ton and *.adnl

This type of links is part of TON DNS and opens up a new world of Web 3.0

There is no need to download third-party wallets and log in to them in order to use TON Proxy. 

Now just click on the "Connect" button and you will immediately activate the proxy server to access the sites of the network *.ton and *.adnl
